    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it feels like a lot of the \"efficiency\" stuff sounds kinda theoretical, though. in the real world, most of the folks i talk to are just worried about staying afloat with all these new mandates. do u think there's a real risk of these guys just being priced out of the market because of the compliance costs?",
